SRA - Now available on the cloud
Sequence Read Archive (SRA) data, available through multiple cloud providers and NCBI servers,
is the largest publicly available repository of high throughput sequencing data. The archive
accepts data from all branches of life as well as metagenomic and
environmental surveys. SRA stores raw sequencing data and alignment information to enhance
reproducibility and facilitate new discoveries through data analysis.
